_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     Computes marginal means (MMs) or average marginal component
     effects (AMCEs) with correction for intra-respondent reliability
     (IRR, tau). When a repeated task is present, IRR is estimated
     unless a fixed value is supplied. Results are returned in a
     structured object ready for plotting and summary.

